%p.style4
  Se ha realizado un pago de un Cash Out.
%p.style4
  %ul
    %li= "Importe: $#{strftime('%.02f', @cash_out.amount)}"
    %li= "Fecha: #{@cash_out.paid_at.strftime('%d/%m/%Y %H:%M:%S')}"
%p.style4
  Para revisar el cash out
  - if @cash_out.user.role == 'influencer'
    = link_to(t('sign_into_your_account'), influencer_cash_out_url(@cash_out))
  - else
    = link_to(t('sign_into_your_account'), affiliate_cash_out_url(@cash_out))
